Key Methodological Decision — Temporal Leakage Fix
The churn label covers February–March 2017.
Without a cutoff, transaction features include is_cancel and is_auto_renew signals from the same window — directly encoding the target.
Result without cutoff: ROC-AUC > 0.97 (inflated, meaningless)
Result with cutoff at 2017-01-31: ROC-AUC ~0.879 (realistic, defensible)
pythonCUTOFF_DATE = pd.Timestamp('2017-01-31')
transactions = transactions[transactions['transaction_date'] <= CUTOFF_DATE]
This is the single most important line in the project.

